div.h3: Create Feature Branch in GitHub and Clone Locally

div.style: text-align: left

ul.li: In GitHub, create feature branch from develop.
Branch naming format to link to PBI:
Replace xxxxx with the PBI number.
Replace pbi-description with a description of the PBI.
This naming format is to accommodate our GitHook.
E.g.feature/AB#12345-add-translated-text
Clone feature branch locally.

div.h3: Commit changes and Push to GitHub

ul.li: Format for commit messages to link to Task:
Replace xxxxx with the Task number.
Replace commit-message with commit message text.
AB#xxxxx will automatically link this commit in Azure Board.
E.g. AB#23456 Update French text on home page
Push local commits to GitHub.
